    "text": "**Vishnu Smriti 56**"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-b1442b",
    "offset": 22,
    "text": "Now, therefore, there are the purifiers of all the Vedas. // Vi_56.1 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-e19c45",
    "offset": 95,
    "text": "By muttering and offering oblations with which, the twice-born are purified from their sins. // Vi_56.2 //"
